  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this study is to determine the prevalence of back pain in permanent
      wheelchair users (excludes transitory users) in different regions of Spain. Another study
      objective is the identification of risk factors for back pain in this population. Data
      collection will be by means of a structured questionnaire which will be validated in a
      previous pilot study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
